<body>
  <h1>Privacy Policy - Glyph Notifications</h1>
  <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 15/03/2025</p>

  <h2>1. Data Collection</h2>
  <p>This app does not collect, store, or share any personal data.</p>

  <h2>2. Access to Installed Apps</h2>
  <p>Glyph Notifications accesses the list of installed apps on your device only to let you choose which apps you want to customize with Glyph notifications. This information is not stored and is never transmitted to any external server.</p>

  <h2>3. Server Communication</h2>
  <p>Glyph Notifications operates entirely locally on your device. No data is sent to a server or shared with third parties.</p>

  <h2>4. Required Permissions</h2>
  <p>The app may request permissions to access notifications and installed apps to function properly. These permissions are used exclusively for the intended features and for no other purpose.</p>

  <h2>5. Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions regarding this privacy policy, feel free to contact us at: <br>
    <a href="mailto:glyphlab.dev@gmail.com">glyphlab.dev@gmail.com</a>
  </p>
